node.text: Shoutout to everyone that follows all of my meme pages. I’m getting a lot of DM’s right now saying I have range because I’m writing RIP shit about Norm Macdonald here, whilmst simultaneously picking a fight w the entire state of Oregon on @floridaman , whilmst aggressively posting frogs because it’s Wednesday on @literallyeverymeme …lol…I still feel like my cult page, @churchofkevinflynn is the perfect meme page at 9 posts tho. IF I SHOW YOU CAN WE BE COOL ABOUT THIS ONE THING WITHOUT PEOPLE CRYING TO ME?! Everyone ready?! NO COMPLAINTS STARTS NOW. OK, so @churchofkevinflynn starts w me being a Jesus like figure. Then I present the bread and wine, and everyone has to choose which one to eat. They both represent my ass. Then I lay down the guidelines of the cult. “The rules are simple: 1. Worship me. 2. You will burn in fucking hell if you don’t.” Pretty standard in every religion. Then I die for everyone’s sin and rise from the dead. Then someone sins again so I have to die again. Then the last post just says “Soon, my children” with a picture of me poorly photoshopped over Jesus’ss’s. Like every religion, it ends with a coming promise that is never actually coming. 55k people eagerly waiting and I plan on never posting on that page ever again. It’s the perfect meme/cult page, and I am the perfect cult leader. I’m like uncomfortably high right now.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kevin Flynn in Sad Boi Hours. May be an image of text that says 'Anthony Jeselnik @anthonyjeselnik Battling cancer for 9 years without telling anyone is the most Norm Macdonald shit ever.'.

node.text: Anthony Jeselnik is in my top 3 favorite comedians, and I feel like that’s rare for some reason. He’s super underrated. I feel like we have the exact same sense of humor. The darker the better. Does anyone that follows me know him personally? I’d love to write with him. I may accidentally end up seducing him tho with my charming personality and HUGE penis. “Kevin, shouldn’t this caption be about Norm Macdonald?” OMG IM SO SORRY. RIP in peace, Norm ♥️😞. Man, this sucks. Fuck cancer. Norm was also one of my favorite comedians. I love people with dry wits. One of my favorite jokes of his is the moth joke. The joke is about a moth that goes into a podiatrist’s office. He then talks about nonsense for however long the person will let him talk. “Why is he in a podiatrists office? He doesn’t have feet.” Then the punchline is “because he left the light on.” I like to study comedians so I’ve seen him tell this joke like 10x and every time the middle part is different. Every time the audience is hanging on to every word, waiting for the inevitable corny line they know is coming whilmst he is just rambling about nonsense. I hope one day my contribution to comedy is 1/100th of what Norm’s was. RIP in peace to one of the best to ever do it ❤️😞 “Isnt this a comedy page?” OMG IM SO SORRY, PENIS PENIS PENIS (meme credit Twitter @anthonyjeselink )

node.text: It’s only Tuesday morning, and I’ve already had two people I haven’t talked to in a decade figure out what I do for a living, DEMAND a free ad immediately, then block/unfollow me when I tell them I have an advertising schedule and have exclusivity contracts I have to follow so I can’t do their ad immediately. THE AUDACITY. Have you ever heard the story of the hen making her bread? No one would help her make the bread, then when it was ready everyone wanted to eat it. Well, the bread is my ass 😩😩 🍑 and everyone wants a bite. FOR REAL THO, this is why I value people in my life SO much that genuinely just want to be my friend with nothing in return. I remember EXACTLY whomst was there for me when I only had $30 in my pocket. I’ve been SCREAMING that I’m the best memer alive since 30k followers and I know EXACTLY whomst supported me. Don’t get me wrong, I’m easily the most loved meme account (like sexually) on earth, but the people that genuinely just love me as a person and don’t want  anything in return are the ones that will get to eat my ass. Or eat my bread**. Or wait, my ass is the bread? Or wait, the bread is hypothetical and my ass is real? Now I’m confused. Alright fine, everyone can eat my ass. Anyway, here’s a meme about Jesus and tattoos. Relevant as hell. Thanks for reading.
